{"title":"Neumonitis por hipersensibilidad-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neumología/Neumonitis por hipersensibilidad-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Neumonitis por hipersensibilidad\\NHipersensibilidad pulmonar","guid":"uIxrDWNr38AEK4cQhwBKrQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Qué es la neumonitis por\\Nhipersensibilidad (NH)?","guid":"GNfIRAVNR4d5-buTMZ9lfg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"R: Es una enfermedad pulmonar intersticial difusa causada por una reacción inflamatoria\\Ninmunomediada a la inhalación repetida de un antígeno en individuos susceptibles. (1)","guid":"hrOA3Vt9v5vuGG2cN8DAqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuáles son los principales\\Nantígenos causales de NH?","guid":"I6NZ782NurlIK-mJLkAp7Q","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"R: Proteínas aviares, hongos, bacterias\\Ntermofílicas y químicos de bajo peso molecular. (1)","guid":"mqjsmFwtI881GCy5r1ntwQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• Enfermedad pulmonar inmunológicamente mediada.","guid":"tjqIZceXWUVBum6g8bYgeA","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• Ocurre en individuos susceptibles.","guid":"ULjqyCF7IiW3HS0SZN0osA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"• Resulta de la inhalación repetida y sensibilización a antígenos\\Nambientales y/o ocupacionales (orgánicos y no orgánicos).","guid":"36fPOu0kOWIuP4ZFq_Psmg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"- Descrita por primera vez en 1713 por Bernardino Ramazzini\\Nen granjeros expuestos a heno mohoso. (2)","guid":"3vI0s4EVUZKM8mIQwt-oYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Características\\NClaves","guid":"bM_W17sR8NyLj3ll0YShxQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• No es una enfermedad atópica o criptogénica.","guid":"oHVecO1wt_STRDQGqwf-RA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Esquema: Neumonitis por\\NHipersensibilidad (HP)","guid":"dR-uO4m3XhfGuqi43aAcaA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"• Antígenos: Variedad\\Namplia (Ver Tabla 1).","guid":"SjhiiGBqyTXsbZxMTGR1mw","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Antígenos Orgánicos:\\NBacterias, Hongos / Levaduras","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Aspergillus spp.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• Fuente: Heno mohoso, ensilaje, grano","guid":"OMWdZ7v2mGB6asnOSvKVoA","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno: Agricultura","guid":"Fbwo63tKM6yC88TRlYHRJw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"• Término de HP: Pulmón del agricultor","guid":"JsQGoK3rVvQmrbLTdlSRQw","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"15","text":"• Thermophillic actinomycetes\\N(Thermoactinomyces vulgaris, T.\\Nsacchari, F. rectovirgula)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Fuente:","guid":"XGKMCq_4ukfZidryUfzmrQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno:","guid":"o9ajAjlKVtn371JKeMD7TQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"• Término de HP:","guid":"x205_Fctze1aOmMcYewFcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"15","text":"• M. avium complex, M.\\Nimmunogenum","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"15","text":"• Fuente: Agua contaminada\\Nde jacuzzis o saunas, fluido\\Nde trabajo en metal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"15","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"15","text":"• Término de HP:\\NPulmón de jacuzzi","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"15","text":"• Alternaria alternata,\\NAureobasidium spp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"15","text":"• Fuente: Sistemas de\\Nhumidificación contaminados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"15","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"15","te