Alternaria spp.,\\NMucor spp.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"82","text":"• Fuente: Hongos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"82","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno:\\NDiversas industrias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"82","text":"• Término de HP:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"82","text":"• Feathers,\\Ndroppings,\\Nserum","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"82","text":"• Fuente: Aves","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"82","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno:\\NIndustria avícola, mascotas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"82","text":"• Término de HP: Pulmón del\\Naficionado a las aves","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"82","text":"• Avian feathers","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"82","text":"• Fuente: Aves","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"82","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno:\\NIndustria avícola","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"82","text":"• Término de HP:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"82","text":"• Rats, gerbils","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"82","text":"• Fuente: Roedores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"82","text":"• Ocupación/Entorno: Laboratorios\\Nde investigación, mascotas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"82","text":"• Término de HP: Pulmón del\\Nmanipulador de roedores","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"- Respuesta inmune exagerada de hipersensibilidad tipo III y IV a la inhalación de antígenos. (1)","guid":"PCYGNPVyPOk2vI9Ud5AwIg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"- Linfocitos T activados y citoquinas proinflamatorias median la respuesta inflamatoria. (1)","guid":"KvrjLVcisViuwD3soqZGEg","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"- La inflamación crónica puede llevar a fibrosis pulmonar irreversible. (1)","guid":"dOU4e4y-74OFv5oIwwurOA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"115","text":"- Potenciales dianas terapéuticas: factores moleculares de la inflamación y fibrosis.","guid":"xOYgaeTxLklCQQqKjQgNtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"- Prevalencia global: 0,5-25,8 casos por 100.000 habitantes. (3)","guid":"pCdD0egxOn7GEzUgb4vsLA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"- En Chile, importante causa de enfermedad pulmonar\\Nocupacional en trabajadores agrícolas y avícolas. (4)","guid":"4e2Dsq08g4LgSZG8hWyBkg","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"- Exposición ambiental u ocupacional a antígenos orgánicos o inorgánicos. (1)","guid":"HX52qqNJFV-W6yCA-pqyqw","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"- Susceptibilidad genética: HLA-DR, TNF-α, TLR. (1)","guid":"qulwms3YnQMPWALHebb6BQ","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"- Tabaquismo\\N(RR: 1,5-3,0). (5)","guid":"8PSaHZglzpD2AZr5fv_Dww","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"Causas:","guid":"XCInJcfHN6Q1vYQyzsUdPQ","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"- Proteínas aviares (pulmón de criador de aves). (1)","guid":"eCHIyZ79LbYadeL0_kPpMQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"- Hongos (pulmón de granjero, silo, trabajador de la madera). (1)","guid":"nsPrUnbgesc6HYKW0uWu1Q","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"- Bacterias termofílicas (pulmón de jacuzzi, pulmón de humidificador). (1)","guid":"XN1nwOHCHE39G66m8sCTGQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"- Químicos de bajo peso molecular (pulmón de trabajador químico). (1)","guid":"GfFH09ix4Dxw3TckaL3UFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"- Alérgica aguda: inicio 4-8 h post-exposición, síntomas \"flu-like\"\\N(fiebre, mialgias, tos seca, disnea), crepitantes finos bilaterales. (1)","guid":"8bw4522bCpAhnN6Cwc4p-Q","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"- Alérgica subaguda: síntomas insidiosos por semanas, tos\\Nseca, disnea de esfuerzo, pérdida de peso, acropaquia. (1)","guid":"1UfhOiUnXhOEYiC-DmoYfg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"- Crónica/fibrosis: disnea progresiva, tos\\Ncrónica, crepitantes finos, cor pulmonale. (1)","guid":"8yYx0CS2quJ2VaKRW6Nkaw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"- Signos de mal pronóstico: disnea severa,\\Nhipoxemia, patrón intersticial extenso en TAC. (1)","guid":"WMAN3FX7ONArWe7DEoiX5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"- Lab: VHS y PCR elevadas, hipergammaglobulinemia, LDH aumentada. (1)","guid":"exuGm54lWcNYew4fiUqQAw","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"- Espirometría: patrón restrictivo. (1)","guid":"hDpZ9zewLsEvET8HZO6AUA","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"137","text":"- DLCO: disminuida. (1)","guid":"pg1AZnJusRkRcj2uL50X1w","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"137","text":"- Rx tórax: patrón\\Nintersticial bilateral. (1)","guid":"7Dr0nGgPimPu99RfxMWBEw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"137","text":"- TAC tórax: opacidades en vidrio esmerilado, micronódulos centrolobulillares, mosaico. (1)","guid":"4kXBuc-4SGvQEV2PeNnjBw","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"137","text":"- Lavado broncoalveolar: linfocitosis (CD8). (1)","guid":"CCxbJn4rFuSKWJH44e38EQ","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"137","text":"- Biopsia: neumonitis intersticial, granulomas no caseificantes, neumocitos hiperplásicos, fibrosis. (1)","guid":"B4wfpO5X5YNIw_aJAGIhMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"- Clínica compatible + exposición a antígeno causal +\\Nhallazgos imagenológicos y patológicos característicos. (1)","guid":"8p64zsqSXH7bpcUr7NWQdQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"- Neumonitis intersticial: sarcoidosis, asbestosis, silicosis. (1)","guid":"8UeIQnVqEokIsx3dyBS_KQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"- Enf. pulmonar intersticial: FPI, NINE, eosinofilias pulmonares. (1)","guid":"LQo45NM7j85HkOyx9296TA","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"- Objetivo: evitar progresión a fibrosis pulmonar.","guid":"SdPKFWBJmPV4URKD8_29iA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"- No farmacológico: evitar exposición al antígeno, cese tabáquico. (1)","guid":"gNv24ALpqtj_AEqhWje8Lg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"- Farmacológico:","guid":"kBycrCvNAkXqwuNpc7mqSg","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"- 1ª línea: prednisona 0,5 mg/kg/d por 4-8 sem, luego disminuir 5-10 mg/sem. (1)","guid":"dKWv7CXtLprzfArtPeL2fw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"- 2ª línea: azatioprina 2-3 mg/kg/d si recaída o corticodependencia. (1)","guid":"Xq42navFelY1y9UzYyvkPA","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"- 3ª línea: micofenolato, rituximab (evidencia limitada). (7)","guid":"jxt1gZdYCjJToJtkfSUQGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"150","text":"- Considerar trasplante pulmonar en fibrosis pulmonar avanzada.","guid":"Y2Hau56aSBjzgCESd_j-NA","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"- Factores de buen pronóstico: diagnóstico y tratamiento\\Nprecoz, mejoría de DLCO en >10% a los 6 meses. (1)","guid":"dO3hBOU0_ypA9MyfSzlr2w","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"- Intervalos de seguimiento según severidad, cada 3-6 meses. (1)","guid":"PX6EndK9P3eP3SSj7LJLHg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"- Monitorizar con espirometrías,\\NDLCO, 6MWT, TAC tórax. (1)","guid":"SvUEVY8AQYHPkDpqcno4rg","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Prevención:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"- Evitar exposición a antígenos causales. (1)","guid":"BccZ8Cg4UTYGLk4JKQfdpg","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"- Educación sobre riesgos a trabajadores expuestos. (1)","guid":"va2w94a9AGLl3T9ZhQUgcA","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"- Uso de equipos de protección personal adecuados. (1)","guid":"yTDJqtSmgg_FjZuzC72B1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"- En trabajadores asintomáticos de alto riesgo. (8)","guid":"zPRZRmcAHSQPNIQwM3T73g","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"- Cuestionarios de síntomas, espirometría anual,\\Nradiografía de tórax (S: 20-80%, E: 80-98%). (8)","guid":"jUDyZya16TZm1EFiH32Gcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"XmDlKJKUBJI7uKBhpct_QQ","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"- Mayor riesgo de NH y peor pronóstico en adultos mayores. (1)","guid":"sejMbR_krnGt04QZaHkU_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"u08S-7Y5phSUDsbsPCyzjg","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"1. Vasakova M, et al. Hypersensitivity\\NPneumonitis: Perspectives in Diagnosis\\Nand Management. Am J Respir Crit Care\\NMed. 2017;196(6):680-689.","guid":"-Al41RyeXvlMCq3dMeB_cQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"2. Ramazzini B. De Morbis\\NArtificum Diatriba. 1713.","guid":"Bj3Rd7ldqwKCtSHr-voUFg","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"3. Pereira C, et al. Hypersensitivity\\Npneumonitis: a complex lung disease.\\NClin Mol Allergy. 2016;14:1.","guid":"R3GEjpFpij0qzuyUrlEX3A","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"4. Contreras G, et al. Enfermedades\\Nrespiratorias ocupacionales en Chile. Rev\\NChil Enferm Respir. 2016;32(1):27-35.","guid":"KP041SOLrfJeR0b0Q5kXUw","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"5. Blanchet MR, et al.\\NHypersensitivity pneumonitis. Allergy\\NAsthma Clin Immunol. 2018;14:80.","guid":"5_9Z9pTQfECO61Y8-VRcBw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"171","text":"6. Richerson HB, et al. Guidelines for the clinical evaluation\\Nof hypersensitivity pneumonitis. Report of the\\NSubcommittee on Hypersensitivity Pneumonitis. J Allergy\\NClin Immunol. 1989;84(5 Pt 2):839-44.","guid":"9m_DAp5TWkGdjg33rO49gg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"171","text":"7. Morisset J, et al. Management of\\NHypersensitivity Pneumonitis. Clin\\NChest Med. 2021;42(4):735-749.","guid":"3xxnDcsgsJV_rjglOxuUlQ","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"171","text":"8. Lara B, Morisset J. Usefulness of Screening\\NQuestionnaires for Hypersensitivity Pneumonitis in\\NExposed Workers. J Allergy Clin Immunol Pract. 2021\\NDec 31:S2213-2198(21)01337-1.","guid":"pATtdAlRipLoZn07NArwVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"0","text":"Abreviaturas:","guid":"-OekxqyRx2p-nWL9YJJeyA","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"- CD8: Cluster de\\NDiferenciación 8","guid":"N4L4CLXwjhPgYXaY2nW54Q","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"- DLCO: Capacidad de Difusión\\Ndel Monóxido de Carbono","guid":"HSy73uEV2r1u6F24iHrecg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"- Enf: Enfermedad","guid":"eG4UD4R0a1XWY40dm4XDsA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"- FPI: Fibrosis\\NPulmonar Idiopática","guid":"3GrFZxaU1z6LwxNqva1QfA","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"- LDH: Lactato\\NDeshidrogenasa","guid":"2xU1o18SlVvE7SdfNosQUg","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"- NINE: Neumonía\\NIntersticial No Específica","guid":"5slkm94LOSoOsdjrJD4z-g","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"180","text":"- PCR: Proteína\\NC Reactiva","guid":"HbKKXFfHoG2xOSe5EltLzQ","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"180","text":"- RR: Riesgo Relativo","guid":"1CuueBHilB2sPTGe4MpuBQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"180","text":"- Sem: Semanas","guid":"oGIg0gKvHNqFuLSVLefnCA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"180","text":"- S: Sensibilidad","guid":"tQZWw7gs4r9OK_sztyGk6Q","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"180","text":"- E: Especificidad","guid":"k9DV_moPGNNIsvzJg9pvsA","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"180","text":"- TAC: Tomografía\\NAxial Computada","guid":"JhpVHSX6ctwjzFzfMjl9Gg","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"180","text":"- TNF-α: Factor de\\NNecrosis Tumoral alfa","guid":"eFca6zBd3g00gLpMS7iQew","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"180","text":"- TLR:\\NReceptor tipo\\NToll","guid":"5DT6S5tsuJjgSHpAyNIaLg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"180","text":"- VHS: Velocidad de\\NHemosedimentación","guid":"OTt3xhcmzNvgzFhCTJh54A","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"180","text":"- 6MWT: Test de\\NCaminata de 6 Minutos","guid":"9cRvIrov5FjI7tbepskf2w","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"0","text":"Hipersensibilidad\\NPulmonar (HP)","guid":"Dl87huRGM1vcub8IYcXLrQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"0","text":"Exclusiones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Fármacos: Asociados a reacciones radiológicas e\\Nhistológicas similares a HP (ej. Enfermedad Pulmonar\\NIntersticial (ILD) con granulomas).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Deben ser excluidos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"0","text":"Incidencia /\\NPrevalencia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• EE.UU.:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• Prevalencia (1 año): 1.67 - 2.71 por 100,\\N000 personas (2004-2013) (1).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"• Incidencia (1 año): 1.28 - 1.94 por 100,\\N000 personas (2004-2013) (1).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"201","text":"• Europa, Medio\\NOriente, India:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"201","text":"• Prevalencia: 2 - 47% en registros de ILD\\N(casos de ILD: 330-2245) (2).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"201","text":"• Incidencia: 0.12 - 0.9 por\\N100,000 personas/año.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"201","text":"• Factores de Variación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"201","text":"• Edad: Aumenta con la edad. Ej: 1.48\\Npor 100,000 (35-44 años) → 11.2 por\\N100,000 (≥65 años) (1).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"201","text":"• Geografía:\\NDiferencias\\Nregionales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"201","text":"• Ocupación: Ciertos trabajos\\Ntienen mayor riesgo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"201","text":"• Estación: Ej: Pulmón del\\Nagricultor prevalente en invierno\\Ntardío y primavera temprana.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"201","text":"• Factores de Riesgo del\\NHuésped: Variabilidad individual.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"0","text":"Formas\\NComunes de\\NHP","guid":"","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"• Pulmón del agricultor:\\NPrevalente en invierno tardío\\Ny primavera temprana.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"• HP relacionada con aves:\\NComún globalmente.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"0","text":"Brotes Ocupacionales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Químicos de bajo peso molecular: Ej:\\NTrabajadores expuestos a fluidos de\\Ntrabajo en metal contaminados.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"• Sistemas de humidificación de\\Nagua: Ej: Brotes en ambientes\\Nlaborales específicos (6).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"0","text":"Presentación Clínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"• Antígeno específico: HP puede ser\\Nespecífica a un antígeno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"• Antígenos múltiples: HP puede reaccionar a\\Nvarios antígenos emergentes de uno o varios\\Nambientes (IA: Inciting Antigen).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"220","text":"• Cese de exposición: La exposición al IA puede haber\\Ncesado antes del reconocimiento de la enfermedad o\\Nevidencia de progresión (7).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"220","text":"• Edad de presentación: Puede ocurrir a cualquier edad,\\Ncon la mayoría de los pacientes presentándose después\\Nde la cuarta década de vida.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"220","text":"• Síntomas respiratorios: Varían\\Nen extensión y severidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"220","text":"• Auscultación pulmonar: Crepitaciones\\Ninspiratorias y/o chillidos inspiratorios\\Nagudos usualmente presentes.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"0","text":"Factores Genéticos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"• Polimorfismos en genes del complejo mayor de\\Nhistocompatibilidad, incluyendo HLA-DR y HLA-DQ,\\Ntransportadores asociados al procesamiento de antígenos,\\Ninhibidores tisulares de metaloproteinasas de matriz,\\Ninmunoproteasomas, y el promotor de TNF-α están asociados\\Ncon una mayor susceptibilidad a HP (8-12).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"• Variantes genéticas comunes en TERC, MUC5B e IVD\\Nestán asociadas con HP fibrótica, mientras que\\Nvariantes genéticas comunes en OB FC1 están\\Nasociadas con HP no fibrótica (13).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"• Telómeros cortos en leucocitos están asociados con\\Ncaracterísticas histopatológicas de neumonía intersticial\\Nusual y supervivencia reducida (14).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"227","text":"• Agrupación familiar de pacientes con HP viviendo en\\Ndiferentes entornos y el desarrollo de HP en gemelos\\Nmonocigóticos ha sido reportado (15).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico y\\NEvaluación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"• Clasificación de HP: Basada en la presencia o ausencia de\\Nfibrosis pulmonar radiológica o histológica, la probabilidad de\\Nexposición al IA, y el nivel de confianza en los hallazgos de\\Nimagen y patología (16, 17).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"• Fibrosis y caracterización del IA:\\NTienen implicaciones para el\\Ndiagnóstico, pronóstico y tratamiento.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"232","text":"• Diagnóstico de HP:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"232","text":"• Exclusión de\\Netiologías\\Nalternativas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"232","text":"• Evaluación\\Nmultidisciplinaria\\Nexhaustiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"232","text":"• HP puede presentarse con\\Nenfisema y en pacientes con\\Ncaracterísticas autoinmunes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"232","text":"• Ninguna prueba única es\\Ndiagnóstica en todos los escenarios.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"232","text":"• Diagnóstico histológico: Ya no se considera el\\Nestándar de oro ni es requerido en todos los casos\\Ndurante el proceso diagnóstico.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación de la\\NExposición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Paso inicial: Caracterizar el tipo(s),\\Nextensión y fuente(s) de exposición\\Nocupacional y ambiental al IA.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"241","text":"• Historia completa y cuestionario de\\Nexposición: Un cuestionario estructurado\\Ndurante la evaluación clínica puede:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"241","text":"• Evitar conclusiones prematuras de una\\Nhistoria de exposición negativa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"241","text":"• Ayudar a la\\Nmemoria del\\Npaciente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"241","text":"• Ahorrar tiempo al\\Ncompletarse antes de la\\Nvisita.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"241","text":"• Asegurar\\Nconsistencia\\N(16).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"241","text":"• Evaluación de casos\\Nsospechosos de HP:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"241","text":"• Historia detallada y uso de un cuestionario\\Nestructurado en evaluaciones periódicas para\\Ndescubrir exposiciones relevantes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"241","text":"• La relación entre la exposición al IA y HP se\\Nbasa en la inferencia causal, como la relación\\Ntemporal de los síntomas con el trabajo y\\Nexposiciones no ocupacionales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"241","text":"• Categorización de la\\Nexposición al IA:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"241","text":"• Identificada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"241","text":"• Indeterminada (evidencia\\Nsugiere una asociación).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"241","text":"• No identificada (16).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"241","text":"• Pruebas inmunológicas específicas de antígenos: No se\\Ndeben usar en casos de HP con exposición identificable al\\NIA, especialmente en pacientes que no desean evitar y\\Neliminar la fuente del antígeno a pesar de las\\Nconsecuencias clínicas adversas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"241","text":"• Resultados negativos pueden\\Napoyar el sesgo del paciente hacia\\Nno evitar el antígeno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"241","text":"• Educación del paciente sobre los\\Nobjetivos de manejo, evitación de\\Nexposición y pruebas es esencial.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"241","text":"• Exposición no\\Nidentificada:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"241","text":"• Ocurre en ~20-50% de los casos,\\Npredominantemente en HP fibrótica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"241","text":"• No excluye el\\Ndiagnóstico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"241","text":"• Historia de mejoría clínica con remediación\\Ndel IA o empeoramiento con reexposición al IA\\Npuede sugerir el diagnóstico de HP, pero su\\Nausencia no lo excluye.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"241","text":"• Consulta con expertos en medicina\\Nocupacional y un higienista ambiental:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"241","text":"• Especialmente cuando se sospecha que la exposición al IA\\Nproviene de un entorno laboral y en pacientes con progresión de la\\Nenfermedad y sospecha de exposición continua indeterminada al IA\\No múltiples fuentes de IA (16).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"0","text":"Pruebas de Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"• Anticuerpos específicos del\\Nantígeno en suero:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"• Métodos\\Ncuantitativos: Ej.\\NELISA.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"264","text":"• Métodos cualitativos:\\NEj. doble difusión.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"264","text":"• Indicativos de exposición previa, pero no\\Nconfirman la presencia de HP.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"264","text":"• Pruebas de\\Nfunción pulmonar:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"264","text":"• No diagnósticas,\\Npero útiles para:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"264","text":"• Cuantificar la severidad del\\Ndeterioro pulmonar subyacente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"264","text":"• Monitorizar la progresión\\Nde la enfermedad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"264","text":"• Evaluar la respuesta\\Nal tratamiento.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"0","text":"Características\\Nde Imágenes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"0","text":"HP No Fibrótica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"• Patrón típico de HP no\\Nfibrótica (Figura 6):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"• Caracterizado por cuatro características mayores en al\\Nmenos un lóbulo y ausencia de características que\\Nsugieran un diagnóstico alternativo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"1. Distribución centrada en pequeñas vías\\Naéreas, involucrando bronquiolos y/o conductos\\Nalveolares (bronquiolocentricidad).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"275","text":"2. Inflamación intersticial celular relativamente\\Ndifusa y uniforme de las paredes alveolares y\\Nbronquiolos (bronquiolitis celular).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"275","text":"3. Inflamación\\Npredominantemente linfocítica\\Ncon pocas células\\Nplasmáticas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"275","text":"4. Granulomas intersticiales mal formados\\Ny/o células gigantes multinucleadas, a\\Nmenudo peribronquiolares.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"275","text":"• Características menores (no\\Ndiagnósticas pero presentes en HP):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"275","text":"• Pequeños focos de\\Nneumonía organizante.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"275","text":"• Macrófagos\\Nespumosos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"275","text":"• Cristales de colesterol.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"275","text":"• Cuerpos de\\NSchaumann.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"275","text":"• Cristales de oxalato\\Nde calcio (16).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"275","text":"• Biopsia compatible con HP\\Nno fibrótica (Figura 7):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"275","text":"• Caracterizada por las tres primeras\\Ncaracterísticas mayores del patrón típico de\\NHP, pero sin granulomas ni características de\\Nun diagnóstico alternativo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"275","text":"• Categoría indeterminada para\\NHP no fibrótica (Figura 8):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"275","text":"• Patrón de EPI que no cumple los criterios para\\NHP no fibrótica, compatible con HP no fibrótica, o\\Nun diagnóstico alternativo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"292","parent":"0","text":"HP Fibrótica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"• **Patrón típico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":293,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neumología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neumología","filename":"Neumonitis por hipersensibilidad-2024","id":"map_1362","resolved_references":[]}